actions.message: Hi Im Ro-Bot, here is A list of Commands:

actions.message:
`!invite` : i will send you an invite link to invite me To your server!
`!clear` : Use this command With a number to clear old messages.Example: (!clear 5)
`!roblox` : Send the link to the Roblox Website!
`!dm` : Dm's The Person you Mentions! Example: (!dm @jake Hi)
`!robux` : Everytime you message something in a channel you get 2 robux! (server currency*)
